FBIS3-43247 "drafr001_c_94011" FBIS-AFR-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 REPUBLIC of SOUTH AFRICA APLA Claims Responsibility MB3112110493 Johannesburg SAPA in English 1056 GMT 31 Dec 93 MB3112110493 Johannesburg SAPA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Cape Town Dec 31 SAPA -- The Azanian People's Liberation Army [APLA], the armed wing of the Pan Africanist Congress, has claimed responsibility for Thursday night's attack on the Heidelburg tavern in Cape Town.
